{"tid":824740,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風過後】何超蓮慈善組織 召集義工清理垃圾","createTime":"2018-09-17T08:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T22:20:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"410c22b5a301b212b68d23721949577c42a52b66","tid":824740,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:08:03.000Z","msg":"颱風「山竹」吹襲香港，樓上遍佈垃圾，行人路被樹枝阻擋。何超蓮的慈善組織就自發性清理路面垃圾，仲喺社交網站召集義工，一齊為香港出一分力！<br />\n<br />\n受到超強颱風「山竹」吹襲，香港遍佈垃圾，民間有人自發性清理街道。藝人何超蓮的慈善組織亦自發性清理路面垃圾，仲喺社交網站召集義工，於受颱風影響嚴重的三個地區：杏花村，將軍澳，沙田，召集義工一起清理道路垃圾。受到網民讚賞！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/160602_63444a12ba3908b1b1757c7e457d208a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F160602_63444a12ba3908b1b1757c7e457d208a.jpg&h=33beb2f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba01ff1b6c4add63985b4f5f7cc2a6b0e66e8b7a","tid":824740,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:09:10.000Z","msg":"巴打們到場未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2150a7941238b2bee986910320dcff2feb290577","tid":824740,"uid":153114,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"清完有冇得屌番劑慰勞下先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085b88ead3364d247817fafc00684a2acf516c69","tid":824740,"uid":160147,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:17:28.000Z","msg":"杏花村，將軍澳，沙田<br />\n<br />\n佢去邊度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8dbae8ebc54e878a646176e7945220c857a1d8","tid":824740,"uid":128219,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:22:00.000